import React from 'react'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import { Table, TableBody, TableRow, TableCell, Typography, Box, Paper } from '@mui/material'; const BatteryDetailsPanel = () => { const battery = useSelector((state: any) => state.battery); return ( <> {"Device Details"} {"Device Type"} {battery.batteryType} {"Floor Dimension"} {battery.batteryFloorWidth + "FT X " + battery.batteryFloorHeight + "FT"} {"Energy"} {battery.batteryEnergy + " MWh"} {"Cost"} {"$" + battery.batteryCost} {"Release Date"} {battery.batteryReleaseDate}
); } export default BatteryDetailsPanel;
